issue.title: [CF 398] Charge and Intercept stun DR
issue.body:
Stuns from charge and intercept are included in the stun DR category, while neither of them has DR or affects DR on other stuns.


> Posted by CurseForge user Ozzrel | Imported from CurseForge issue #398 | Raw

comments.body:
TellMeWhen obtains its DR categories from http://www.wowace.com/addons/drdata-1-0/

If there is an issue with incorrect spells, you need to report it there for it to be fixed in TMW.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras

Is there anyone still working on it? It hasn't been updated for quite a while.


> Posted by CurseForge user Ozzrel

Post a ticket and see what happens.


> Posted by CurseForge user Cybeloras
